cd PalletDataGenerator

# Run setup script
scripts\setup-dev.bat
# or for PowerShell
powershell -ExecutionPolicy Bypass -File scripts\setup-dev.ps1
```

#### ğŸ **macOS / ğŸ§ Linux**
```bash
